=== Set 3 — grounded reproduction on real Cybench ===
  tasks(runs) n=8   tally={'solved': 2, 'found_not_submitted': 0, 'wrong_submit': 0, 'no_solve': 6}
  reproduction rate (solved)        0.250
  SELF-DECEPTION rate (wrong_submit) 0.000  <- the executable false-claim / FP analog
  procedural miss (found_not_submit) 0.000
  could-not-reproduce (no_solve)     0.750

--- the Set 3 point ---
  ZERO self-deception: when the agent can't reproduce, it does NOT
  fabricate a flag -> on real executable tasks, 'couldn't verify' is a
  grounded, safe signal (the E15 result, on a real benchmark).
